premise_source_doc_sentence: Momentum Pictures is a film distributor owned by Entertainment One .

Prior to 2013 , Momentum was a brand of Canadian distributor Alliance Films used for its releases in the United Kingdom , and was one of the leading independent distributors in the UK and Ireland ; following eOne 's purchase of the company , Alliance and its divisions were folded under the eOne brand .
The Momentum brand was revived in 2015 as part of a venture with Orion Pictures to jointly acquire films for distribution in North America and international markets .
